data.description: Adorable home with large lot and sitting on the end of a quiet street. Nice one level, 4 bedroom, 2 bath home.  There is a detached garage with a lien to and a wood shed. House was originally a duplex but was remodeled in the 2000's and update to a single family residence.  Metal roof installed approximately 5 years ago.
